AUTHOR: andretoth
CONTENT: I came into this thinking Olivia was just some industry pop starlet (admittedly I was a fan of the song vampire) dime a dozen type but I had no idea how much depth and emotion and incredible quality her music had. This is exactly why Tiny Desk is such magic it helps you see through the smoke and mirrors of industry production and showcases the talent of the artists in its purest form. I'm now an Olivia Rodrigo fan!
